'From Squeak2.9alpha of 13 June 2000 [latest update: #3016] on 15 November 2000 at 3:17:33 pm'!"Change Set:		ScorePlayerFitDate:			15 November 2000Author:			Andreas RaabMake the score player #shrinkWrap rather than #spaceFill."!!ScorePlayerMorph methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'ar 11/15/2000 15:16'!initialize	super initialize.	self listDirection: #topToBottom.	self wrapCentering: #center; cellPositioning: #topCenter.	self hResizing: #shrinkWrap.	self vResizing: #shrinkWrap.	self layoutInset: 3.	color _ Color veryLightGray.	self borderWidth: 2.	self onScorePlayer: (ScorePlayer new initialize) title: ' '.	self extent: 20@20.! !